name: Moors of Ykesha
description: This huge ancient swamp is the chief base of operations for the Gunthak Pirates, and the ancestral homeland for the frogloks of Norrath. Places of legend, such as the ruins of Guk and the city of Grobb can be found here, as well as anchors to the alternate dimension known as the Void.
